     C                     ENDIF
     C                     ENDDO
     C                     ENDSR
     C*================================================================
     C*
     C           #WRITE    BEGSR
     C                     MOVE *BLANK    B8SKBN           DELETE CD
     C                     Z-ADD0         B8SKYY           DELITE DATE YY
     C                     Z-ADD0         B8SKMM                       MM
     C                     Z-ADD0         B8SKDD                       DD
